{
  "__comment": "EuroTransit SLO overview — presents the team-ratified checkout success and latency objectives, error-budget burn, alert state, and controlled load shedding. Prometheus retains 7d while the SLO window is 30d, so the fixed-window summary panels are explicitly labelled as 7d evidence rather than official 30d compliance.",
  "title": "EuroTransit — SLO overview",
  "uid": "eurotransit-slo",
  "tags": ["eurotransit", "slo", "error-budget", "burn-rate"],
  "timezone": "browser",
  "schemaVersion": 39,
  "refresh": "1m",
  "time": { "from": "now-6h", "to": "now" },
  "links": [
    {
      "asDropdown": false,
      "icon": "external link",
      "includeVars": false,
      "keepTime": true,
      "targetBlank": false,
      "title": "Order lifecycle",
      "tooltip": "Open the async workflow dashboard",
      "type": "link",
      "url": "/d/eurotransit-order-lifecycle/order-lifecycle"
    }
  ],
  "templating": { "list": [] },
  "panels": [
    {
      "id": 1,
      "type": "text",
      "title": "SLO contract and available evidence",
      "gridPos": { "h": 4, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 0 },
      "options": {
        "mode": "markdown",
        "content": "### Ratified checkout objectives\n**Success:** ≥ 99% of `POST /orders` responses are non-5xx over 30 days. **Latency:** p95 < 500 ms over 30 days. HTTP 429 is controlled load shedding and does not consume the success error budget.\n\n**Retention caveat:** Prometheus currently retains **7 days**, so the summary stats below are labelled **7d evidence** and must not be presented as official 30-day compliance. The 5m / 1h / 6h multi-window burn-rate alerts are fully supported by current retention."
      }
    },
    {
      "id": 2,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Success rate — available 7d",
      "description": "Seven-day evidence against the ratified >=99% target. This is not the official 30-day SLO evaluation because Prometheus retains only 7d.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "decimals": 3,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 99 },
              { "color": "green", "value": 99.5 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none", "justifyMode": "auto", "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "100 * (1 - (sum(increase(http_server_requests_seconds_count{namespace=\"eurotransit\", job=\"eurotransit-orders\", uri=\"/orders\", method=\"POST\", status=~\"5..\"}[7d])) or vector(0)) / clamp_min(sum(increase(http_server_requests_seconds_count{namespace=\"eurotransit\", job=\"eurotransit-orders\", uri=\"/orders\", method=\"POST\"}[7d])), 1))",
        "instant": true,
        "refId": "A"
      }]
    },
    {
      "id": 3,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Checkout p95 — available 7d",
      "description": "Seven-day p95 evidence against the ratified 500ms target. The histogram is scoped to POST /orders on the stable Orders service.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "decimals": 3,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "green", "value": null },
              { "color": "yellow", "value": 0.35 },
              { "color": "red", "value": 0.5 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none", "justifyMode": "auto", "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (increase(http_server_requests_seconds_bucket{namespace=\"eurotransit\", job=\"eurotransit-orders\", uri=\"/orders\", method=\"POST\"}[7d])))",
        "instant": true,
        "refId": "A"
      }]
    },
    {
      "id": 4,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Error budget remaining — 7d proxy",
      "description": "Request-based proxy: 100% means none of the 1% budget was used in the available 7d; 0% means the 7d error ratio is at or above 1%. Not the official 30-day budget.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "decimals": 1,
          "thresholds": {
            "mode": "absolute",
            "steps": [
              { "color": "red", "value": null },
              { "color": "green", "value": 0.001 }
            ]
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none", "justifyMode": "auto", "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "100 * clamp_max(clamp_min(1 - (((sum(increase(http_server_requests_seconds_count{namespace=\"eurotransit\", job=\"eurotransit-orders\", uri=\"/orders\", method=\"POST\", status=~\"5..\"}[7d])) or vector(0)) / clamp_min(sum(increase(http_server_requests_seconds_count{namespace=\"eurotransit\", job=\"eurotransit-orders\", uri=\"/orders\", method=\"POST\"}[7d])), 1)) / 0.01), 0), 1)",
        "instant": true,
        "refId": "A"
      }]
    },
    {
      "id": 5,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "429 share — available 7d",
      "description": "Controlled refusals as a share of POST /orders. Ratified policy excludes 429 from the error-budget numerator, but this panel keeps degradation visible.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 4 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 0,
          "max": 100,
          "decimals": 2,
          "color": { "mode": "fixedColor", "fixedColor": "orange" }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none", "justifyMode": "auto", "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "100 * (sum(increase(http_server_requests_seconds_count{namespace=\"eurotransit\", job=\"eurotransit-orders\", uri=\"/orders\", method=\"POST\", status=\"429\"}[7d])) or vector(0)) / clamp_min(sum(increase(http_server_requests_seconds_count{namespace=\"eurotransit\", job=\"eurotransit-orders\", uri=\"/orders\", method=\"POST\"}[7d])), 1)",
        "instant": true,
        "refId": "A"
      }]
    },
    {
      "id": 6,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Fast burn alert",
      "description": "CheckoutErrorBudgetFastBurn requires >14x burn on both 5m and 1h windows. FIRING is a page-now condition.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 0, "y": 9 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "min": 0,
          "max": 2,
          "mappings": [{
            "type": "value",
            "options": {
              "0": { "text": "OK", "color": "green", "index": 0 },
              "1": { "text": "PENDING", "color": "yellow", "index": 1 },
              "2": { "text": "FIRING", "color": "red", "index": 2 }
            }
          }]
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none", "justifyMode": "center", "textMode": "value" },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "(max(ALERTS{alertname=\"CheckoutErrorBudgetFastBurn\", alertstate=\"pending\"}) or vector(0)) + 2 * (max(ALERTS{alertname=\"CheckoutErrorBudgetFastBurn\", alertstate=\"firing\"}) or vector(0))",
        "instant": true,
        "refId": "A"
      }]
    },
    {
      "id": 7,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Slow burn alert",
      "description": "CheckoutErrorBudgetSlowBurn requires >6x burn on both 1h and 6h windows. FIRING is a business-hours ticket condition.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 6, "y": 9 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "min": 0,
          "max": 2,
          "mappings": [{
            "type": "value",
            "options": {
              "0": { "text": "OK", "color": "green", "index": 0 },
              "1": { "text": "PENDING", "color": "yellow", "index": 1 },
              "2": { "text": "FIRING", "color": "red", "index": 2 }
            }
          }]
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none", "justifyMode": "center", "textMode": "value" },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "(max(ALERTS{alertname=\"CheckoutErrorBudgetSlowBurn\", alertstate=\"pending\"}) or vector(0)) + 2 * (max(ALERTS{alertname=\"CheckoutErrorBudgetSlowBurn\", alertstate=\"firing\"}) or vector(0))",
        "instant": true,
        "refId": "A"
      }]
    },
    {
      "id": 8,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "Checkouts — available 7d",
      "description": "Total POST /orders responses observed by the stable Orders ServiceMonitor in the available retention window.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 12, "y": 9 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "color": { "mode": "fixedColor", "fixedColor": "blue" }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none", "justifyMode": "auto", "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "sum(increase(http_server_requests_seconds_count{namespace=\"eurotransit\", job=\"eurotransit-orders\", uri=\"/orders\", method=\"POST\"}[7d])) or vector(0)",
        "instant": true,
        "refId": "A"
      }]
    },
    {
      "id": 9,
      "type": "stat",
      "title": "5xx failures — available 7d",
      "description": "POST /orders responses that consume the ratified success-rate error budget.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 5, "w": 6, "x": 18, "y": 9 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "decimals": 0,
          "color": { "mode": "fixedColor", "fixedColor": "red" }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "colorMode": "background", "graphMode": "none", "justifyMode": "auto", "textMode": "auto" },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "sum(increase(http_server_requests_seconds_count{namespace=\"eurotransit\", job=\"eurotransit-orders\", uri=\"/orders\", method=\"POST\", status=~\"5..\"}[7d])) or vector(0)",
        "instant": true,
        "refId": "A"
      }]
    },
    {
      "id": 10,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Checkout success rate — 5m rolling",
      "description": "Short-window view of the same success SLI used by the burn-rate rules. The 99% line is the ratified target, not an additional alert.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 0, "y": 14 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "percent",
          "min": 95,
          "max": 100,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false
          }
        },
        "overrides": [{
          "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "99% target" },
          "properties": [
            { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red" } },
            { "id": "custom.lineStyle", "value": { "fill": "dash", "dash": [10, 10] } },
            { "id": "custom.fillOpacity", "value": 0 }
          ]
        }]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "100 * (1 - (eurotransit:checkout_error_ratio:rate5m or vector(0)))",
          "legendFormat": "checkout success",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "vector(99)",
          "legendFormat": "99% target",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 11,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Checkout latency — p95 rolling 5m",
      "description": "POST /orders p95 against the ratified 500ms objective. Scoped to the stable Orders service, matching the SLI definition.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 12, "x": 12, "y": 14 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "s",
          "min": 0,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false
          }
        },
        "overrides": [{
          "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "500ms target" },
          "properties": [
            { "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red" } },
            { "id": "custom.lineStyle", "value": { "fill": "dash", "dash": [10, 10] } },
            { "id": "custom.fillOpacity", "value": 0 }
          ]
        }]
      },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "histogram_quantile(0.95, sum by (le) (rate(http_server_requests_seconds_bucket{namespace=\"eurotransit\", job=\"eurotransit-orders\", uri=\"/orders\", method=\"POST\"}[5m])))",
          "legendFormat": "checkout p95",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "vector(0.5)",
          "legendFormat": "500ms target",
          "refId": "B"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 12,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Error-budget burn rate — multi-window",
      "description": "Burn rate = error ratio / 1% budget. Fast page requires both 5m and 1h above 14x; slow ticket requires both 1h and 6h above 6x. The 1x line is the sustainable long-term rate.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 9, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 22 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "short",
          "min": 0,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 8,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false
          }
        },
        "overrides": [
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byRegexp", "options": "/.*threshold|sustainable.*/" },
            "properties": [
              { "id": "custom.lineStyle", "value": { "fill": "dash", "dash": [10, 10] } },
              { "id": "custom.fillOpacity", "value": 0 }
            ]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "14x fast threshold" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "red" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "6x slow threshold" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "orange" } }]
          },
          {
            "matcher": { "id": "byName", "options": "1x sustainable" },
            "properties": [{ "id": "color", "value": { "mode": "fixed", "fixedColor": "green" } }]
          }
        ]
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true } },
      "targets": [
        {
          "expr": "(eurotransit:checkout_error_ratio:rate5m or vector(0)) / 0.01",
          "legendFormat": "5m burn",
          "refId": "A"
        },
        {
          "expr": "(eurotransit:checkout_error_ratio:rate1h or vector(0)) / 0.01",
          "legendFormat": "1h burn",
          "refId": "B"
        },
        {
          "expr": "(eurotransit:checkout_error_ratio:rate6h or vector(0)) / 0.01",
          "legendFormat": "6h burn",
          "refId": "C"
        },
        {
          "expr": "vector(1)",
          "legendFormat": "1x sustainable",
          "refId": "D"
        },
        {
          "expr": "vector(6)",
          "legendFormat": "6x slow threshold",
          "refId": "E"
        },
        {
          "expr": "vector(14)",
          "legendFormat": "14x fast threshold",
          "refId": "F"
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": 13,
      "type": "timeseries",
      "title": "Checkout outcomes and load shedding",
      "description": "Response rate by status. 5xx consumes error budget; 429 is separately visible controlled refusal; 200 includes idempotent replay and 202 is a newly accepted workflow.",
      "gridPos": { "h": 8, "w": 24, "x": 0, "y": 31 },
      "datasource": { "type": "prometheus", "uid": "prometheus" },
      "fieldConfig": {
        "defaults": {
          "unit": "reqps",
          "min": 0,
          "custom": {
            "drawStyle": "line",
            "lineInterpolation": "linear",
            "lineWidth": 2,
            "fillOpacity": 10,
            "showPoints": "never",
            "spanNulls": false
          }
        },
        "overrides": []
      },
      "options": { "legend": { "displayMode": "table", "placement": "bottom", "showLegend": true } },
      "targets": [{
        "expr": "sum by (status) (rate(http_server_requests_seconds_count{namespace=\"eurotransit\", job=\"eurotransit-orders\", uri=\"/orders\", method=\"POST\"}[2m]))",
        "legendFormat": "HTTP {{status}}",
        "refId": "A"
      }]
    }
  ]
}
